  "description": "Ghanaian Ewe Agbadza dance rhythm: atsimevu master drum, sogo and kidi support, axatse shaker approximation via beatbox hi-hat. Polyrhythmic 12/8 with 33% swing.",
  "tags": [
    "prism",
